name: tables Angelo Cappellini
description: Since 1886, the company Angelo Cappellini creates furniture in the style of Brianza and is known around the world for the game models of major European styles: Louis XV, Louis XVI, Regency, Empire and Biedermeir. The company has its roots in the past, but much focused on the future, and serves clients around the world with a catalog of unique products that exceeds one thousand pages.
